  "body": "### Description\n[comment]: # (Feature or Bug? i.e Type: Bug)\n_Type_: Bug\n\n[comment]: # (Describe the feature you would like, or briefly summarise the bug and what you did, what you expected to happen, and what actually happens. Sections below)\n_Summary_: PIN screen is shown on Chats tab after user returns from PIN screen to sign a message in the DApp and taps on Chats tab\n\n#### Expected behavior\n[comment]: # (Describe what you expected to happen.)\nlist of Chats is shown (or some opened chat)\n\n#### Actual behavior\n[comment]: # (Describe what actually happened.)\nPIN screen is shown\n\n### Reproduction\n[comment]: # (Describe how we can replicate the bug step by step.)\nVideo: https://drive.google.com/open?id=1thgsPdxlsqCN4zQyppuVXQxt44n9G_k5\nWhile on Ropsten network:\n\n* Open Status and sign in with keycard\n* Switch to DApps tab, scroll to the very end and tap on Status Test Dapp\n* in Test DApp: tap on Transactions -> Sign message. As a result, Sign message screen will be shown\n* tap on Sign\n* DO NOT enter PIN. Tap on \"<\" button in top left corner to return to the Dapp\n* tap on Chats icon\n\n### Additional Information\n[comment]: # (Please do your best to fill this out.)\n\n* Status version: 0.12.0 apk http://status-im-prs.ams3.digitaloceanspaces.com/StatusIm-190402-123212-80ef5d-pr.apk\n* Operating System: Android 9, Pixel XL\n\n#### Logs\n[comment]: # (if on Android please replicate bug whilst running adb logcat)\n[Status.log](https://github.com/status-im/status-react/files/3039711/Status.log)\n\n",
